WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
A mother raccoon stands near a tree.

00:04.000 --> 00:09.000
A baby raccoon reaches toward the trunk.

00:09.000 --> 00:14.000
The baby begins climbing carefully.

00:14.000 --> 00:19.000
The mother watches closely.

00:19.000 --> 00:25.000
The baby climbs higher up the tree.
